## OmitTypeSchema interface

TypeScript `Omit` type, represents omit some properties from a interface.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export interface OmitTypeSchema 
```

## Remarks

See: [https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/utility-types.html\#omittype-keys](https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/utility-types.html#omittype-keys)

## Example


```ts
interface AAA {
    a: string,
    b: string,
    c: string
}

// Equivalent to `{ c: string }`
type BBB = Omit<AAA, 'a' | 'b'>;

```
